    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "A true project car with classic appeal, this one is best suited for someone looking for a restoration candidate or a parts car with potential. It has the kind of vintage character enthusiasts appreciate, but it does need significant work before it will be ready to enjoy. If you\u2019ve been searching for an honest fixer-upper at an approachable price, this could be a worthwhile starting point.",
