    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Project-priced and honestly represented, this is a complete, usable classic for someone who wants an affordable entry point and doesn\u2019t mind taking on a rough car. It has appealing style and solid enthusiast potential, but it is firmly a poor-condition example with noticeable cosmetic wear, age, and likely mechanical needs before it can be considered a dependable driver. Best suited for a handy buyer, restoration candidate, or someone looking for parts/value rather than a turn-key car.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept vehicle in good overall condition and a solid choice for someone looking for dependable transportation without paying top dollar for a showroom-level example. It presents nicely inside and out, with typical age-related cosmetic wear but no major red flags in how it shows. The interior is tidy, the exterior still looks respectable, and overall it has clearly been maintained and driven with normal use in mind. Buyers should expect a good, honest used vehicle that is ready to be enjoyed as a daily driver.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older car in poor overall condition and best suited for a project, restoration candidate, or parts donor. It is showing heavy age and wear throughout, with notable cosmetic deterioration, a tired interior, and the likelihood of deferred maintenance and mechanical needs. This is not a car to describe as turn-key; buyers should expect faults, repairs, and a thorough going-over before relying on it regularly. That said, it is an affordable entry point for someone who wants a fixer-upper and understands what comes with a rough, driver-needing example.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical option for commuting, errands, or as a starter vehicle. A sensible choice for someone who appreciates a low entry cost and solid everyday utility.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect at this price, but it still offers solid value and a chance to get into a car without breaking the bank. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind a little TLC, this could be a really smart buy.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Budget-friendly driver with strong project potential. This car is in poor cosmetic and overall condition, but it still offers a usable powertrain, straightforward mechanical layout, and the kind of platform that makes sense for someone who wants inexpensive transportation or a hands-on weekend revival. Expect visible wear, age-related flaws, and general roughness throughout, but for the right buyer it\u2019s an affordable way into a capable chassis with plenty of life left for light duty, parts use, or restoration-minded ownership. Priced to move and worth a look if you know what you\u2019re after.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
